    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Java 8 introduced CompletableFuture, available in the package java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture, which can be used to make an async call :</p>\n<pre><code>CompletableFuture.runAsync(() -&gt; {\n    // method call or code to be async.\n});\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 362885,
        "reputation" : 40074,
        "user_id" : 706317,
        "user_type" : "registered",
        "accept_rate" : 70,
        "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/1mafF.jpg?s=256",
