    "question_id" : 1842734,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Java 21+:</p>\n<pre><code>Thread.ofVirtual().start(() -&gt; {\n    // Some work\n});\n</code></pre>\n<p>Or (if you don't want a virtual thread for some reason):</p>\n<pre><code>Thread.ofPlatform().start(() -&gt; {\n    // Some work\n});\n</code></pre>\n"
